<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d195hn26-ptr" id="PJA13d195hn26">hn26</a>

   <p>(1) Generaal der vereenigde</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d195hn27-ptr" id="PJA13d195hn27">hn27</a>

   <p>
 <del title="deleted text">&lt;(2) van Europa&gt;</del>
 <a class="ptr" href="" id="PJA13d195n13-ptr">13</a>
</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA13d195hn28-ptr" id="PJA13d195hn28">hn28</a>

   <p>([<ins title="added">2</ins>]<del title="deleted text">&lt;3&gt;</del>) aldaar</p>

